{
  "stem": "198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 70.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In panic, you do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw people are jumping, so I jumped, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked into Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a family in Lodz, my cousin Masza and her family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Which, she had five siblings, and she is the youngest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we stayed in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After a while, I don't know how, my mother and father came to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When my mother came, she could not jump the train, so the Germans rounded her up and guarded her with German Shepherds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She stood all night in 10 degrees below zero.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She came to Lodz [SOBBING] frozen-- frozen hands, frozen legs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I could not recognize the way she looked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After a while, we reunited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] they gave us a little apartment in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] It had no floors, had no windows, had no facilities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody had a bathroom, nobody had running water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But at least we all were together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Going back-- I have to go back. 1939, a friend of my father's came to my father and said, I went to a city meeting, and they saying that they going to deport all the young people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So my father took my brother which was 18 years old, and the German friend got him down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We lived on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Got him out from the city, and he was heading to the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was still before, this was in 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got him out, and I remembered that my father and mother stood on the top of the stairs and they-- they said, just play cool.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't say goodbye, because it will be too obvious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, he left to Russia, and he was there for six years.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
